The paper discusses the development and deployment of Autonomous Vehicles (AVs) and focuses on the high-level software component responsible for decision-making in an AV. This suggests that the paper is likely to belong to the Artificial Intelligence (cs.AI) and Robotics (cs.RO) sub-categories. Additionally, the paper discusses the formal verification of the AV agent's behaviour, which suggests that it may also belong to the Software Engineering (cs.SE), Systems and Control (cs.SY), and Machine Learning (cs.LG) sub-categories.
